<article class="row hentry post-240457 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail tag-corporate-media tag-donald-trump tag-economy tag-in-the-news tag-interview tag-noam-chomsky tag-north-korea tag-politics section-politics-and-elections primary_topic-politics" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle">
