<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/noam-chomsky-on-the-populist-groundswell-us-elections-the-future-of-humanity-and-more/">Noam Chomsky on the Populist Groundswell, US Elections and the Future of Humanity</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Noam Chomsky on where we stand as an economy, as a country and as human beings.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/lynn-parramore/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Lynn Parramore</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://www.ineteconomics.org/perspectives/blog/noam-chomsky-on-the-populist-groundswell-u-s-elections-the-future-of-humanity-and-more' itemprop='url'>Institute for New Economic Thinking</a></span></dd>
</dl>
<time class="published updated meta-data" datetime="2018-03-23T04:00:00+00:00" itemprop="datePublished dateCreated" content="2018-03-23T04:00:00+00:00">March 23, 2018</time>
